務，保護個人數據隱私；依法設立金融控股公司；完善公司治理；依法合規開展證券基金業務。潘功勝表示，螞蟻要充分認識到整改的嚴肅性和必要性，盡快制定方案和實施時間表，金融管理部門將與螞蟻保持密切溝通。<br />\n<br />\n潘功勝指，螞蟻作為金融科技和平台經濟領域具有重大影響力的企業，必須自覺遵守國家法律法規，將企業發展融入到國家發展大局中，切實承擔企業社會責任，強調未來會堅決打破壟斷，糾正、查處不正當競爭行為，堅持所有金融活動必須依法依規納入監管，金融業務必須持牌經營，對各類違法違規行為零容忍。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2372366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2372366&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=9abb3bc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2372366</a>"},{"pid":"c868575c3e1b83413a4e1ac3fad1d4fa12ff5c05","tid":2342543,"uid":108146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cdb18964b986728057a5f08bea1f7df35f5b32e","tid":2342543,"uid":52684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />股價都唔止跌咗10%啦 可以反彈未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:05:36.000Z","msg":"沒收所有, drop to 0"},{"pid":"75197fd64c52f49ce6e4c03a6b51284063695d4b","tid":2342543,"uid":232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ccdf2f1ad0c5c23e782995baabe15a80621521e6","tid":2342543,"uid":293677,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淘寶係咪就黎收皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />創造造多失業人口<br />\n石頭.腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"唔會收皮,繼續做生意,仲越做越大<br />\n不過變咗國企<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aabe7464b92517ea96c60edf590e1f0b34fa27","tid":2342543,"uid":66202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a966298c32d0be3f4da98abcd69955402017fbe9","tid":2342543,"uid":76310,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ccdf2f1ad0c5c23e782995baabe15a80621521e6","tid":2342543,"uid":293677,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"<i